FT  09 JUL 92 / Forte: Correction
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
IN THE FT yesterday, we reported that Forte was one of four companies
reprimanded by the Financial Reporting Review Panel for deviations from
accounting standards. In fact, the review panel said it was satisfied with
Forte's explanations in respect of four matters brought to its attention,
and had concluded there was no cause for action. We regret the error.
