FT  09 JUL 92 / Observer: Howdo, pardner?
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The success rate of husband-and-wife teams in retailing is scarcely one to
threaten wholesale redundancy among marriage guidance counsellors.
Admittedly, Body Shop's Anita and Gordon Roddick appear to have made a
triumph of both business and married life. But they are very much the
