arrangement' with his creditors. Mr George Auger, of accountants Stoy
Hayward, was appointed to act as his nominee in seeking the arrangement.
The order 'stays' all existing or pending civil proceedings against Mr
Maxwell for 14 days to allow him to prepare voluntary settlement proposals
for consideration by his nominee.
