FT  08 JUL 92 / Observer: Sleep easy
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
New UK environmental regulations require industry to use BATNEEC to clean up
its act. This stands for best available technology not entailing excessive
cost. Industry has responded with CATNIP - cheapest available technology not
involving prosecution.
